# code-only, so `graphify update .` needs no LLM API key. Graphify classifies
# .md/.mdx/.qmd/.txt/.rst/.html/.yaml/.yml/.pdf + images as "docs" requiring
# semantic (LLM) extraction — excluded here on purpose.

# --- Doc / markup / data formats (would demand an LLM key) ---
